{"tid":2239280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以幫男朋友分擔下情緒","createTime":"2020-10-11T19:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T05:30:28.000Z","uid":153877,"like":4,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc9d854d358f27949f26add8420c45f1594296a","tid":2239280,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T19:09:36.000Z","msg":"第一次開po，有咩事大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事源琴日成日見男朋友悶悶不樂咁，已經feel到唔對路，講嘢嘅内容同同佢互動一直都好小心。 <br />\n<br />\n我依嫁同佢一齊住，琴日半夜兩個都瞓唔到佢話肚餓出廳食嘢。之後我就奇點解佢咁耐未返房所以出去睇下佢。點知我見到佢係apps搵人傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/nap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我又上嗰個apps到搵返佢出嚟。因為嗰一下見到佢無啦啦用apps我嚇親，我以為佢想搵女傾計。<br />\n<br />\n之後俾我係apps搵到佢，佢話想上網搵人淨係9up下放負。我就問佢點解唔同我傾，有咩事我都想同佢分擔，唔想佢自己一個人咁。 之後佢話我已經夠負<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想再放我負，同埋話女朋友係拎嚟錫。 <br />\n<br />\n想知我要點樣做先可以分擔下佢d情緒。 我頹個時佢就陪住我，我唔想佢頹個時得自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好想俾佢知有咩事有人會陪住佢<br />\n<br />\n係未男人就真係有咩事都自己收收埋埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申： 同男朋友係apps識，但堅信佢唔會帽我"},{"pid":"75dd5e0c635061aaee7373bd300d63c6b0d38cee","tid":2239280,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"咩apps"},{"pid":"5c1b35bdd7db1662ce1a8d9a2bb085a1d78d29de","tid":2239280,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75dd5e0c635061aaee7373bd300d63c6b0d38cee","tid":2239280,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"咩apps"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T19:11:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8279eb7910f114c746975ee6cfcc6c728e29d82","tid":2239280,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c1b35bdd7db1662ce1a8d9a2bb085a1d78d29de","tid":2239280,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75dd5e0c635061aaee7373bd30